### Welcome to nofdev Pages.
This site is for DevOps troubshooting.

### About MAAS provisioning on bare metal
When using MAAS as a fresh install, the command `maas maas nodes accept-all` is invalid. When you do not execute the command, you will see the declaration node on the MAAS web UI as well.
